summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 4.4°C) and outside temperature (up 3.3°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 9%) and rainfall (up 0.5 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 622 m), light levels (up 3408 lux), and pressure (up 11 mbar).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 7138 lux) and cloud levels (up 1026 m) when compared to today.
